@Injectable({
    providedIn: "root"
})
export class DeletePuzzleServiceService {
    public prepareReturnIcon(): HTMLImageElement {
        const returnIcon = "data:image/svg+xml;base64,";
        const img = new Image();
        img.src = returnIcon;
        return img;
    }
    public returnPuzzle(manageGraphicsService: ManageGraphicsService): fabric.ControlMouseEventHandler {
        return (eventData: MouseEvent, transform: fabric.Transform): boolean => {
            const puzzleFabricImage = transform.target as fabric.Image;
            const boardCanvas = puzzleFabricImage.canvas;
            if (boardCanvas !== undefined) {
                if ("_objects" in puzzleFabricImage) {
                    ((puzzleFabricImage as any)._objects as fabric.Image[]).forEach((puzzleImage: fabric.Image) => {
                        manageGraphicsService.removeFromBoard(puzzleImage, boardCanvas);
                    });
                    boardCanvas.discardActiveObject().requestRenderAll();
                }
                else {
                    manageGraphicsService.removeFromBoard(puzzleFabricImage, boardCanvas);
                    boardCanvas.discardActiveObject().requestRenderAll();
                }
            }
            else {
                console.log("Error: canvas is undefined - cant return puzzle from board!");
            }
            return true;
        };
    }
}
